      "comment": "DIVERGENCES FROM THE SOURCE TREE (US-045). (1) Two of Piyomon's six Champions are dropped for want of art: Kokatorimon is absent from the asset pack entirely, and Nanimon exists only as a single idle frame, so neither may be named by an edge (docs/sprite-availability.md). (2) Coelamon and Mojyamon belong to the V4 tree's OTHER rookie, Palmon, but the existing palmon line in this file is the classic Palmon -> Togemon -> Lilimon line, not V4's, so they are attached here instead of going unseeded. (3) That leaves five Champions and four energy types, as with Patamon. The tree's unearned Champion is Nanimon, which cannot be seeded, so the isDefault slot has no natural occupant: Kuwagamon takes it, sharing Leomon's strength gate from below on minEnergy and maxCareMistakes. A well-raised strength Piyomon still reaches Leomon.",
